## What to do

### 1. JSON-LD structured data in layout.tsx
Add a <script type="application/ld+json"> tag inside the <head> (or as a child of <html> before <body>) with Organization schema:

```tsx
<script
  type="application/ld+json"
  dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{
    __html: JSON.stringify({
